Oh Nurse R  or who ever you are....<br><br>
Adios.  <br><br>
Nothing need be said, no matter how desperate you are for a reply.  AHH, Shit, I can't help it. So here's the last mention of you, from me, and I hope you re-read it a few times, so that you will understand it.<br><br>
I offered you a challenge, in parting, tell all those students you are helping to write me an e-mail about you, (without your censorship), about what they think of you and what your beliefs are.   I will post a summary about you, based soley on their writing. Same offer goes for your wife to join in.  If you are the greatest teacher since Moses, than I will sincerely add my apology.  If you are as I suspect, and others, than your leaving this site will be like nothing, because you have nothing, gave nothing, and thought nothing. <br><br>
You are right, our &quot;precious cybertime&quot; is not worthy of you, so  Sleep well, safe in the knowledge that you protested with our vote, while hundreds of your generation died, you &quot;taught&quot; tough students while the rest of us faced PTSD, Prison, Forced Immigration, bar-room insisted haircuts, and lives forever changed by those simple 7 letters: viet nam.  E-mail me anytime you want some more truth.  And lastly, Retched, stop hiding behind the white skirts of a nom de plume, you insult every women who served, let alone every woman who is a nurse, past and present.<br><br>
Ah the beauty of cyberspace (and life) , you never existed.<br><br>
